The **~BlogJournal** [[Help:WikiPlugin|plugin]] includes the latest blog entries for the current users blog if signed, or the ADMIN_USER's blog if not.

== Usage ==

{{{
<<BlogJournal>>
}}}

== Arguments ==

{| class="bordered"
|-
! Argument
! Description
! Default value
|-
| **count**
| Number of entries
| empty
|-
| **user**
| Blog of given user
| empty
|-
| **month**
| List the blog titles per month
| empty
|}

== Example ==

{{{
<<BlogJournal>>
}}}

<<BlogJournal>>

